1. You need to have libusb +universal and cmake installed.
sudo ./get-osx-port-install-prereq_sudo-run-this

2. You need to buid libfreenect
./build-libfreenect
cd libfreenect/build
sudo make install

3. You need to build the freenect driver
./build-freenect-driver

4. You need to get the default installations
./get-necessary-zips

5. And put everything together
./assemble-working-freenect-nite
